#. Tag: title
#: man-okular.1.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "Okular User's Manual"
msgstr "Uporabniški priročnik Okular"

#. Tag: author
#: man-okular.1.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<firstname>Yuri</firstname><surname>Chornoivan</surname> <contrib>Okular man "
"page.</contrib> <email>yurchor@ukr.net</email>"
msgstr ""
"<firstname>Yuri</firstname><surname>Chornoivan</surname> <contrib>Okular man "
"page.</contrib> <email>yurchor@ukr.net</email>"

#. Tag: date
#: man-okular.1.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "2022-02-19"
msgstr "19.02.2022"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: man-okular.1.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "Okular 22.04"
msgstr "Okular 22.04"

#. Tag: productname
#: man-okular.1.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid "KDE Gear"
msgstr "KDE Gear"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-okular.1.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"

#. Tag: refname
#: man-okular.1.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>okular</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>okular</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-okular.1.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "a universal document viewer"
msgstr "univerzalni pregledovalnik dokumentov"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-okular.1.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>okular</command> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>Okular options</"
"replaceable></arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>URL</replaceable></arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>okular</command> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>Okular možnosti</"
"replaceable></arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>URL</replaceable></arg>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-okular.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>okular</command> is aimed to show documents in different formats."
msgstr ""
"<command>okular</command> je namenjen prikazovanju dokumentov v različnih "
"formatih."

#. Tag: title
#: man-okular.1.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Okular options"
msgstr "Okular možnosti"

#. Tag: option
#: man-okular.1.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "-p, --page <replaceable>number</replaceable>"
msgstr "-p, --page <replaceable>število</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open a page with a given number in the document."
msgstr "Odpri stran s podano stranjo v dokumentu."

#. Tag: option
#: man-okular.1.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "--presentation"
msgstr "--presentation"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start the document in presentation mode."
msgstr "Zaženite dokument v predstavitvenem načinu."

#. Tag: option
#: man-okular.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "--print"
msgstr "--print"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start with print dialog."
msgstr "Začni s pogovornim oknom za tiskanje."

#. Tag: option
#: man-okular.1.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "--print-and-exit"
msgstr "--print-and-exit"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start with print dialog and exit after printing."
msgstr "Začni s pogovornim oknom za tiskanje in zapusti po tiskanju."

#. Tag: option
#: man-okular.1.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "--unique"
msgstr "--unique"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unique instance control."
msgstr "Edinstveni nadzor primerkov."

#. Tag: option
#: man-okular.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "--noraise"
msgstr "--noraise"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows to prevent Okular window raising after the start."
msgstr "Omogoča preprečitev dviga okna Okularja po začetku."

#. Tag: option
#: man-okular.1.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "--find <replaceable>string</replaceable>"
msgstr "--poišči <replaceable>niz</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tries to find and highlight a given string in the document. Only works if "
"just one document is given as an argument of the okular command."
msgstr ""
"Poskuša najti in označiti dani niz v dokumentu. Deluje le, če je podan samo "
"en dokument kot argument ukaza okular."

#. Tag: option
#: man-okular.1.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "--editor-cmd <replaceable>string</replaceable>"
msgstr "--editor-cmd <replaceable>niz</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the external editor command. You cannot set the editor command in an "
"already running Okular instance. Please note that <option>--unique</option> "
"is not supported when setting the editor command at the commandline."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi ukaz zunanjega urejevalnika. Ukaza urejevalnika ne morete nastaviti "
"v že delujočem primerku Okularja. Upoštevajte, da <option>--unique</option> "
"ni podprt pri nastavljanju ukaza urejevalnika v ukazni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: man-okular.1.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arguments"
msgstr "Argumenti"

#. Tag: option
#: man-okular.1.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "<option>URL</option>"
msgstr "<option>URL</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An address of the document to be opened. For PDF, can be given as "
"<replaceable>document_name</replaceable>#<replaceable>named_destination</"
"replaceable> where <replaceable>named_destination</replaceable> is a "
"particular named destination embedded in the document."
msgstr ""
"Naslov dokumenta, ki ga želite odpreti. Za PDF se lahko poda kot "
"<replaceable>ime_dokumenta</replaceable>#<replaceable>ime_cilja</"
"replaceable>, kjer je <replaceable>ime_cilja</replaceable> določen imenovani "
"cilj, vdelan v dokument."

#. Tag: title
#: man-okular.1.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Feedback"
msgstr "Povratne informacije"

#. Tag: para
#: man-okular.1.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On IRC, irc.libera.chat #okular or via email, okular-devel@kde.org or on the "
"web, &lt;<ulink url=\"https://okular.kde.org/\">https://okular.kde.org/</"
"ulink>&gt;."
msgstr ""
"Na IRC, irc.libera.chat #okular ali po e-pošti, okular-devel@kde.org ali na "
"spletu, &lt;<ulink url=\"https://okular.kde.org/\">https://okular .kde.org/</"
"ulink>&gt;."

#. Tag: title
#: man-okular.1.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "Glej tudi"

#. Tag: member
#: man-okular.1.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More detailed user documentation is available from <ulink url=\"help:/okular"
"\">help:/okular</ulink> (either enter this <acronym>URL</acronym> into "
"&konqueror;, or run <userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> "
"<parameter>help:/okular</parameter></userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnejša uporabniška dokumentacija je na voljo na <ulink url=\"help:/"
"okular\">help:/okular</ulink> (bodisi vnesite ta <acronym>URL</acronym> v "
"&konqueror; ali zaženite <userinput><command> khelpcenter</command> "
"<parameter>help:/okular</parameter></userinput>)."

#. Tag: member
#: man-okular.1.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "kf6options(7)"
msgstr "kf6options(7)"

#. Tag: member
#: man-okular.1.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "qt6options(7)"
msgstr "qt6options(7)"

#. Tag: member
#: man-okular.1.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also further information available at <ulink url=\"https://okular."
"kde.org/\">https://okular.kde.org/</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Dodatne informacije so na voljo tudi na <ulink url=\"https://okular.kde.org/"
"\">https://okular.kde.org/</ulink>"

